<h2>Pro techniky</h2>

<p>TrekMap běží na HTML4.01, PHP{=phpversion()}, JavaScriptu a frameworku <a href="http://www.nettephp.com">Nette</a> s <a href="http://www.dibiphp.com">dibi</a>. Systém podporuje <a href="http://www.openid.net/">OpenID</a>, <a href="http://www.gravatar.com/">Gravatar</a> a <a href="http://www.microformats.org/">mikroformáty</a>.
Využitá API: <a href="http://www.amapy.cz/">Amapy.cz</a>, <a href="http://www.vyskopis.cz/">Výškopis ČR</a>, <a href="http://www.geonames.org/">GeoNames</a>, <a href="http://code.google.com/intl/cs/apis/chart/">Google Chart API</a>, <a href="http://code.google.com/intl/cs/apis/maps/documentation/services.html#Geocoding">Google Maps API</a>,
<a href="http://code.google.com/intl/cs/apis/maps/documentation/staticmaps/">Google Static Maps API</a>. Ikonky jsou z <a href="http://tango.freedesktop.org/">projektu Tango</a>, <a href="http://www.pinvoke.com/">Fugue Icons</a> a <a href="http://semlabs.co.uk/journal/sem-labs-web-blog-icon-pack">SEM Labs Web Blog Icon Pack</a>.</p>

